channel.title: My First Gframe
channel.description:
Mod please move if in wrong spot, I do not exactly know what section in clients to add this to. Thanks :) Ok, I know people have made a lot better Gframes then this, but I wanted to try one for fun...
[b]Estimated Time: 30 Minutes
Please, do not flame.. Tell me how I can improve it[/b] if you want to :D This is kind of a Wooden theme, as I only used wood textures.
[img]http://img505.imageshack.us/img505/1171/fm77s6.png[/img]
Yes, i Know it looks hidious :( Just wanted to let you guys know what you think about it.
